<Link id="l00195" /><CodeLine lineNumber="195"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Parse the machine basic block definitions, and skip the machine</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00196" /><CodeLine lineNumber="196"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// instructions.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00197" /><CodeLine lineNumber="197"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00198" /><CodeLine lineNumber="198"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// This function runs the first parsing pass on the machine function&#39;s body.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00199" /><CodeLine lineNumber="199"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// It parses only the machine basic block definitions and creates the machine</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00200" /><CodeLine lineNumber="200"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// basic blocks in the given machine function.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00201" /><CodeLine lineNumber="201"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00202" /><CodeLine lineNumber="202"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The machine instructions aren&#39;t parsed during the first pass because all</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00204" /><CodeLine lineNumber="204"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// resolve the machine basic block references.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00205" /><CodeLine lineNumber="205"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00206" /><CodeLine lineNumber="206"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Return true if an error occurred.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00207" /><CodeLine lineNumber="207"><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a46e5b5618c54f98506becf5e4878b626">parseMachineBasicBlockDefinitions</a>(<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/perfunctionmiparsingstate">PerFunctionMIParsingState</a> &amp;PFS,</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00209" /><CodeLine lineNumber="209"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00210" /><CodeLine lineNumber="210"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Parse the machine instructions.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00211" /><CodeLine lineNumber="211"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00212" /><CodeLine lineNumber="212"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// This function runs the second parsing pass on the machine function&#39;s body.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00213" /><CodeLine lineNumber="213"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// It skips the machine basic block definitions and parses only the machine</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00214" /><CodeLine lineNumber="214"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// instructions and basic block attributes like liveins and successors.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00215" /><CodeLine lineNumber="215"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00216" /><CodeLine lineNumber="216"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The second parsing pass assumes that the first parsing pass already ran</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00217" /><CodeLine lineNumber="217"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// on the given source string.</span></CodeLine>
